description:
DC & Karlous are both back in the studio. A lot has happened in the past few weeks so they made sure to touch on it all. RIP to Prince, Lemonade and Jay-Z, adding some respeck to Birdman's name and finally DC takes us to church. Subscribe, download, RT and share. Then leave a comment. #85SouthShow
